---
Source:
  - Title: Treasury of Traditional Wisdom
    Page: 30
By: William Law
Tags:
  - Creation=Inexhaustibility of the Creator
  - Reality
---
And here you may behold the sure ground of the absolute impossibility of
the annihilation of the soul. Its essences never began to be, and
therefore can never cease to be; they had an eternal reality before
they were in or became a distinct soul, and therefore they must have the
same eternal reality in it.
